Note:

* Every bullet below provides (first) a direct link to the audio excerpt (on github) as well as a link to the original episode on freakonomics.com with time information
* Until [Airr](https://www.airr.io/) becomes available for Android I am going to have to manually extract passages from podcasts that I really like, sigh.
Maybe the required substantial manual work acts as a filter for not overloading this page.

